## üßæ Quick Recap

| Component | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| ZTNA | Zero trust access model |
| Identity | New security perimeter |
| Connector | Publishes internal apps |
| Policy Engine | Access decisions |
| App-Level Access | No network exposure |

