## ‚ö° In Simple Terms

Old world:
Connect to VPN ‚Üí roam entire network.

Cloud world:
Prove identity ‚Üí access one app.

No private IP exposure.  
No lateral movement.  
No blind trust.

ZTNA doesn‚Äôt secure networks.  
It deletes them.

